room_title: Escape room "The Conjuring" by Panic Escape Room in Chicago
review: My daughter and her friends had a great time celebrating her 13th birthday by doing the Panic escape room! Lots of shouts, giggles and screams were had but overall they escaped and are already talking about doing it again as soon as possible!
